    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts exactly as it should, making for a very reliable driving experience. While the exterior paint still has a great shine, you will notice some minor road wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. The interior is clean and free of odors, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it\u2019s a dependable, attractive car that is ready for its next home.",
