    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant factory shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no significant curb rash, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free. The leather seating is supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, while the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All technological features, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and premium audio system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It features a complete service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. The engine runs smoothly without any hesitation, and the transmission provides seamless shifts. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system flush and a new cabin air filter. This is a solid, honest example of a driver's car that requires nothing but a new garage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Boasting a well-preserved exterior and a refined interior, it offers a premier driving experience for the discerning buyer seeking exceptional value and long-term reliability.",
