      "description": "This 997.1-generation Carrera features a mid-mounted 3.6L flat-six engine, delivering linear power through a precision 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by a multi-link rear suspension and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for exceptional damping control. Braking is handled by four-piston monoblock calipers paired with cross-drilled, ventilated rotors, ensuring minimal thermal fade. The hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern electric systems lack. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent inspection of the IMS bearing and rear main seal to ensure mechanical longevity.",
